CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 10, 1962, pg. 13A reads: "At AKA Founders Day - Members of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority celebrated Founders Day last Sunday at Loendi Club. Nearly 60 members of the sorority attended the event.  Officers of the group are seen standing in rear.  They are, left to right: Elizabeth McCombs, Merline Stewart, Nan Currington, basileus; LaRue Frederick, regional director; Juanita Alston and Reba Ginyard. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority members, including standing in rear, from left: Elizabeth McCombs, Merline Stewart, Nan Moone Currington, LaRue Frederick, Juanita Alston, and Reba Ginyard, gathered at two long banquet tables, in Loendi Club, another version
